<h3>7、高度相等的列</h3>
如果您使用两个CSS列，以此来作为他们完全一样的高度
<blockquote><pre lang="javascript">$(document).ready(function() {  
function equalHeight(group) {  
    tallest = 0;  
    group.each(function() {  
        thisHeight = $(this).height();  
        if(thisHeight > tallest) {  
            tallest = thisHeight;  
        }  
    });  
    group.height(tallest);  
}  
// how to use  
$(document).ready(function() {  
    equalHeight($(".left"));  
    equalHeight($(".right"));  
});  
}); </pre></blockquote>
<h3>8、简单字体变大缩小</h3>
